701770f-a.text:
Sedgwicl Avenue, east side, at Dndercliff Avenue, showing the wall erected by the Works Progress Administration, which separates the two thoroughfares. Dndercliff Avenue, ascends
the incline on the far side of the wall.
Jan. 13, 1937
